text: There is a boy on the stool. The stool is tipping over. The boy is taking cookies out of the jar. The cupboard is open. The girl is saying, putting her finger to her mouth and also putting her hand out for a cookie. The mother is washing dishes. Water is spilling over from the sink onto the floor. The window is open. The drapes are open. There are two cups and a saucer on the sink. She is stepping on the water on the floor. She is drying the dishes and she is looking outside at the trubbery. The boy is handing the girl a cookie. The girl is holding the cookie. The girl is holding the cookie. The girl is holding the cookie.
